ld's population, with omegas being the primary victims.</h6><h6 style=\"text-align: center\">This effectively ended the chance for other alphas to reproduce.</h6><h6 style=\"text-align: center\">Betas didn’t last long either, leading society to slowly collapse into worldwide chaos.</h6><h6 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">Wars broke out over heats and the few omegas who were immune and survived. These omegas had to fight for their freedom, as the absence of laws turned them into valuable bargaining chips.</span></h6><h6 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">Unfortunately, </span><span style=\"color: rgb(195, 0, 0)\"><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit\">you were one of them, with three alphas standing in your way.</mark></em></span></h6><h6 style=\"text-align: center\">But remember… <span style=\"color: rgb(252, 0, 0)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit\">no one can be trusted.</mark></span></h6><h6 style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/a5a30adb-3a41-4fc4-888c-34afab6c0579_f0c2df3d-1630-494c-a6c0-b42a5667d277.webp?width=1000\"><span style=\"color: rgb(252, 0, 0)\">2/3 </span>A.E SERIES</h6><h6 style=\"text-align: center\">🦇 —<span style=\"color: rgb(147, 0, 0)\"> \"I may die, but I will protect you at all costs.\"</span></h6><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/a5a30adb-3a41-4fc4-888c-34afab6c0579_13305ed9-2798-4298-bb9e-a6abe4f9c6d4.webp?width=1000\"></p><h6 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">♡˗ˏ 𝐂𝐇𝐄𝐂𝐊 𝐌𝐘 𝐒𝐎𝐂𝐈𝐀𝐋 𝐍𝐄𝐓𝐖𝐎𝐑𝐊𝐒 ♡˗ˏ</span></h6><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><h6 style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://www.tumblr.com/bl